# Project Brief: WM2 Distribution Marketing Website

## Project Overview
A modern, responsive 3-page static website for WM2 Distribution Marketing company built with React and TypeScript. The website is designed to showcase products and services with a professional, modern interface.

## Core Requirements
- **Home Page**: Main landing page with hero section, features, and call-to-action
- **About Us Page**: Company information, mission, and team details
- **FAQ Page**: Frequently asked questions with expandable accordion interface
- **Responsive Design**: Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
- **GitHub Pages Hosting**: Published and accessible online

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend**: React 19.1.1 with TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS via CDN
- **Routing**: React Router DOM 7.8.0
- **Build Tool**: Vite 6.2.0
- **Hosting**: GitHub Pages
- **Repository**: https://github.com/mohanad-alsharef/wm2-distribution-marketing-publish

